{"tid":1233902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課","createTime":"2019-06-16T23:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:49.000Z","uid":93479,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8757435612828fffbbc6ebf7f1a6f03d539f85f5","tid":1233902,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:27:40.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4R3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=1857bae4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 不死守任何公共空間<br />\n近年全球各地都流行佔領公共空間運動，縱然有助團結抗爭者，令其有平台公開表達訴求，但佔領運動始終有其缺點，一味據守陣地會虛耗資源和精力，民氣隨時間消耗，又更容易成為鎮壓目標。<br />\n<br />\n黃背心示威者反其道而行，不死守任何公共空間，在每個星期六湧上街頭，沒有任何既定路線，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路，用各種直接行動撼動政權。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，讓汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。"},{"pid":"59e0b34fb13a85f50790fd2045763a21fb3b164b","tid":1233902,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:30:28.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"72010d91fafc2206a3d322af67f04edd767b7ef5","tid":1233902,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:52:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"41edcf7ae7f40f05789aefe6774c7c88ecff69e6","tid":1233902,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}